Know The Olin Story

A merger here. An acquisition there. Add in a lot of innovation and dedication to customers, and you have the catalyst for what is the world’s only global chlorinated organics manufacturer.
Learn More
 
 
 
 







You Can Rely on Our Secure Solvent Supply

Through our reliable and sizeable distribution network, you have access to standard and formulated products that will scale to meet your volume needs, from drums to totes to barges, virtually anywhere in the world.
View Products
 
 
 
 







Intermediates with a High Consistency of Quality and Supply

With a full portfolio of intermediates and as the most reliable global supplier, we are able to deliver the quality you need without the delivery interruptions often found in smaller scale operations. 
